# Product Requirements Document (PRD)
**Project:** 9point75 Woodworks LLC Website
**Owner:** Russ / 9point75 Woodworks LLC
**Target Launch:** April 30

## Objective
- Attract home and furniture clients
- Generate custom quote requests
- Position the brand as high-end, handcrafted, and professional

## Target Audience
- Homeowners seeking custom furniture or cabinetry
- Clients interested in heirloom-quality pieces
- Budget range: $200 - $25,000, with positioning toward higher-end work
- Geographic focus: Northeastern North Carolina, with travel and delivery available

## Core Launch Features
- Text-led homepage with process, trust signals, and clear CTA
- Filtered gallery with no project detail pages at launch
- About page with personal story and philosophy
- Contact / quote form with uploads
- Protected admin route for one owner account

## Technical Direction
- Custom Next.js site on GitHub -> Vercel
- Domain purchased on Cloudflare
- Supabase for auth, storage, and quote submissions
- Strong mobile-first focus
- Quiet veteran-owned positioning

## Content Direction
- Draft homepage copy from scratch
- Gallery uses placeholders until final photos are ready
- Budget range guidance belongs in the form, not as hard pricing
